OL,3,CArrest made after man left in
OL,4,C'critical condition' in alleyway
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FA man has been arrested following a
OL,8,Freport of an assault in an Abertillery
OL,9,Falleyway, police have confirmed.
OL,11,FA 60-year-old man is in a critical
OL,12,Fcondition in hospital after suffering
OL,13,Fa head injury in an alleyway off
OL,14,FDivision Street at about midnight, on
OL,15,FMonday, 4 May.
OL,17,FA 55-year-old man has been arrested
OL,18,Fand remains in police custody being
OL,19,Fquestioned.
